%% seq_08a_project_create_member_add.mmd
%% Scope: Create project and add project member.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Org Member
    participant B as Browser
    participant C as Controller
    participant Cmd as Command
    participant Rules as ProjectRules
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Evt as Event Bus

    Note over U, Evt: CREATE PROJECT
    U->>B: Fill project form
    B->>C: POST /projects
    C->>Cmd: CreateProjectCommand
    Cmd->>Rules: Validate dates and project status
    Cmd->>Repo: save(project)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT projects
    Cmd->>Repo: save owner membership
    Repo->>DB: INSERT project_members
    Cmd->>Evt: emit(project:created)
    C-->>B: Redirect to project page

    Note over U, Evt: ADD PROJECT MEMBER
    U->>B: Add member to project
    B->>C: POST /projects/members
    C->>Cmd: AddProjectMemberCommand
    Cmd->>Repo: Check organization membership
    Repo->>DB: SELECT organization_users

    alt Target user is not approved org member
        Cmd-->>C: Reject request
        C-->>B: Validation error
    else Approved org member
        Cmd->>Repo: save project member
        Repo->>DB: INSERT project_members
        Cmd->>Evt: emit(project:member_added)
        C-->>B: Redirect back
    end
